<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brimful" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brimful,</orth> full to the top: <cit><quote>our legions are b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.215" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 215</bibl></cit>. Followed by <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>b. of sorrow,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 14</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his eye b. of tears,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 1, 67</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. of fear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.214" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 214</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>